query:
SELECT
                    event_id as "event_id: _",
                    event_payload as "event_payload: _"
                FROM webhook_subscription_events
                    WHERE subscription_id = $1
                         AND (cast($2 as INT8) IS NULL or event_id > $2)
                         AND (cast($3 as INT8) IS NULL or event_id <= $3)
                    ORDER BY event_id
